title: Video Evidence Proves The Censors Are Full Of It (Ep 1700)
description:
In this episode I address the hard evidence that the people trying to censor Joe Rogan, and others, are full of it. 

News Picks:


GoFundMe is in a world of trouble for what they did to the truckers. 


Support for Rogan is growing in the free speech crowd.


Spotify CEO speaks out again about Rogan.

COVID cases are dropping as the latest Omicron wave appears to ebb. 


Rumble is exploding in popularity.
